headline: India's Modi meets Qualcomm CEO; discusses AI and innovation
summary: "Great to see Qualcomm's commitment towards India's semiconductor and AI missions," Modi said in a post on X.  On Friday, China initiated an investigation into the U.S. semiconductor manufacturer over its acquisition of Israel's Autotalks, China's market regulator said.
